.SH ENVIRONMENT
.
.TP
.B \%VISUAL\ / \%EDITOR
The values of \%\fBVISUAL\fR and \%\fBEDITOR\fR environment variables determine the text editor for editing script files, and when opening configuration files with \%\fB--config\fR.
.IP
